{{Otheruses|Artom}}
"'''After Artom'''" (A.A) was a system of [[Time/Legends|time]] calculation used in the [[Cularin system/Legends|Cularin system]] to measure [[Standard year/Legends|years]]. [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]] and [[Almas]] both used this method to calculate the passage of time. The calculations began with the rediscovery of the Cularin [[Star system/Legends|system]] by [[Reidi Artom]] in [[232 BBY/Legends|232 BBY]].

